Critical security patterns identified in code review: (1) skip_security_check bypass flags must be #[serde(skip)] to prevent external input bypass, (2) path traversal prevention requires memory ID validation and path canonicalization, (3) secret detection patterns need regular updates for new formats (sk-proj-*, Azure, Vault tokens), (4) audit loggers must never debug-print potentially sensitive content.